{# Google AdSense responsive banner — visually contained.
   Included on list/aggregation pages (home, category, tag, featured, new).
   NOT on game detail pages (keep reviews ad-free for reading).
   slot: 7984158181, client: ca-pub-1115845392526625

   The container gives the slot a clear "Sponsored" label + hairline border so
   it reads as an intentional ad placement rather than a broken widget,
   regardless of which creative the network serves. #}
<aside class="my-8 surface rounded-2xl p-3 sm:p-4" aria-label="Sponsored">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-2 px-1">Sponsored</p>
    <ins class="adsbygoogle block w-full"
         style="display:block; min-height:90px"
         data-ad-client="ca-pub-1115845392526625"
         data-ad-slot="7984158181"
         data-full-width-responsive="true"></ins>
    <script>
        (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
    </script>
</aside>
